<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>How Web Experts Make Your Website User-Friendly – Web EASY Experts</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    /* ── Design tokens (same as main site) ── */
    :root {
      --red: #E53935;
      --red-lt: #FFEBEE;
      --red-dk: #B71C1C;
      --bg: #F8FAFC;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --subtle: #F1F5F9;
      --muted: #E2E8F0;
      --t900: #0F172A;
      --t700: #334155;
      --t500: #64748B;
      --t300: #CBD5E1;
      --border: #E2E8F0;
      --r-md: 0.25rem;
      --r-lg: 0.35rem;
      --r-xl: 0.5rem;
      --sh-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
      --sh-md: 0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
      --sh-lg: 0 12px 40px rgba(15,23,42,.12);
      --display: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      --body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--body);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--t700);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      color: var(--t900);
      line-height: 1.25;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       WBEASY-BLOG-PG — Blog Post Page
       All classes prefixed: .wbeasy-blog-pg-*
    ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */

    /* ── Main layout ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-layout {
      padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem;
    }

    /* Sidebar sticky wrapper */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-sidebar-sticky {
      position: sticky;
      top: 88px;
    }

    /* ── Article ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-article {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--sh-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── Post Header ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-post-header {
      padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    /* Category badge */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cat-badge {
      background: var(--red-lt);
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    /* Title */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-title {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--t900);
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-title span { color: var(--red); }

    /* Meta */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-av {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: var(--red);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-name {
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t900);
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-role { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--t500); }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-sep { width: 1px; height: 22px; background: var(--border); }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-item { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--t500); }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-item i { font-size: 0.7rem; }

    /* Tags */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--t500);
      background: var(--subtle);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0.18rem 0.65rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tag:hover { background: var(--red-lt); color: var(--red); border-color: #FFCDD2; }

    /* Content body */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-body {
      padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-post-header { padding: 1.25rem; }
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-body { padding: 1.25rem; }
    }

    /* ── Blog image placeholder ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      height: 340px;
      background: var(--subtle);
      border: 2px dashed var(--border);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(229,57,53,0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          45deg,
          transparent,
          transparent 20px,
          rgba(226,232,240,0.4) 20px,
          rgba(226,232,240,0.4) 21px
        );
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-icon {
      width: 60px; height: 60px;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-icon i {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--t300);
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-label {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--t300);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-sub {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--t300);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder { height: 200px; }
    }

    /* Intro paragraph */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-intro {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--t700);
      line-height: 1.8;
      border-left: 3px solid #E53935;
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Section heading */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-h2 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--t900);
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-h2::before {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 4px;
      height: 1.2em;
      background: #E53935;
      border-radius: 0;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-h3 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t900);
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    /* Paragraph */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-p {
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      color: var(--t700);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* Tip box */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tip {
      background: #FFF8F8;
      border: 1px solid #FFCDD2;
      border-left: 4px solid #E53935;
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tip i {
      color: #E53935;
      font-size: 1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tip-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--t700);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-tip-text strong { color: var(--t900); }

    /* Bullet list */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--t700);
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 0.3rem 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-list li i {
      color: #E53935;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* Info cards grid — for industry section */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card {
      background: var(--subtle);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(229,57,53,0.3);
      box-shadow: var(--sh-md);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon.mi-red   { background: #E53935; }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon.mi-blue  { background: #2563EB; }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon.mi-green { background: #16A34A; }
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon.mi-amber { background: #D97706; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-title {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t900);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-card-desc {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--t500);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Dark highlight section */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box {
      background: #0F172A;
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(229,57,53,0.1), transparent 70%);
      top: -100px; right: -80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box-title {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box-title span { color: #E53935; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: #CBD5E1;
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 0.35rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list li i {
      color: #4ADE80;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    /* Divider */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    /* Share + CTA bottom bar */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-bottom-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-share-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t500);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn {
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--t500);
      background: var(--white);
      transition: all 0.2s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn:hover {
      background: #E53935;
      color: #fff;
      border-color: #E53935;
    }

    /* CTA Button */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: #E53935;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 0;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-btn:hover {
      background: #B71C1C;
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* ── Featured Image ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #0F172A 0%, #1a2a4a 40%, #0F172A 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    /* Color accent strip on top */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #E53935, #2563EB, #16A34A, #D97706);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    /* Grid overlay texture */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      background: rgba(229,57,53,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.3);
      color: #FF8A88;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-headline {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      max-width: 560px;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-headline span {
      color: #E53935;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-icons {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-icon-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-icon-item i {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-icon-item span {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* Red glow blob */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 350px; height: 350px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(229,57,53,0.12), transparent 70%);
      top: -80px; right: -80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-glow-2 {
      position: absolute;
      width: 250px; height: 250px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37,99,235,0.08), transparent 70%);
      bottom: -60px; left: -40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* ── Sidebar ── */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-sidebar {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    /* CTA widget */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget {
      background: #0F172A;
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 3px solid #E53935;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      background: rgba(229,57,53,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(229,57,53,0.2);
      border-radius: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-icon i { color: #FF8A88; font-size: 1.1rem; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-title {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.97rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-title span { color: #E53935; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-sub {
      font-size: 0.77rem;
      color: #64748B;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-btn {
      display: block;
      background: #E53935;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-btn:hover { background: #B71C1C; color: #fff; }

    /* Author widget */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-author-widget {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: var(--sh-sm);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-author-av {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: var(--red);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-author-name {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t900);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-author-role {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--t500);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-author-bio {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--t500);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* Related posts widget */
    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-widget {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: var(--sh-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-head {
      padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--subtle);
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-head i { color: #2563EB; font-size: 0.9rem; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-head span {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--t900);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item:hover { background: var(--subtle); }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-thumb {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item-title {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.79rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--t900);
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item:hover .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item-title { color: #2563EB; }

    .wbeasy-blog-pg-related-item-meta {
      font-size: 0.69rem;
      color: var(--t500);
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-sidebar-sticky { position: static; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-layout { padding: 1.5rem 0 3rem; }
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; }
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img { height: 220px; }
      .wbeasy-blog-pg-featured-img-icons { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>



<!-- ══════ BLOG LAYOUT ══════ -->
<section class="wbeasy-blog-pg-layout">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row g-4">

      <!-- ── Main Content ── -->
      <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="500">
        <article class="wbeasy-blog-pg-article">

          <!-- Post Header inside article -->
          <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-post-header">

            <!-- Badge -->
            <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-cat-badge mb-3 d-inline-flex"><i class="bi bi-laptop me-1"></i> Web Design</span>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h1 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-title">How Web Experts Make Your Website <span>User-Friendly</span></h1>

            <!-- Meta -->
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta d-flex align-items-center flex-wrap gap-3 mt-3">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-av">WE</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-name">Web EASY Experts</div>
                  <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-role">Web Design Team · India</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-sep d-none d-sm-block"></div>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-item d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-1"><i class="bi bi-calendar3"></i> June 2025</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-item d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-1"><i class="bi bi-clock"></i> 8 min read</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-meta-item d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-1"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Web Design</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Tags -->
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">User Experience</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">Web Design</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">Responsive Design</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">SEO</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">Performance</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">WordPress</span>
              <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tag">Shopify</span>
            </div>

          </div><!-- /post-header -->

          <!-- Body -->
          <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-body">

            <!-- Blog Image Placeholder -->
          <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder">
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-image"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-label">Blog Image</div>
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-img-placeholder-sub">1200 × 630 recommended</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Intro -->
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-intro">
              Web Experts play a critical role in creating a website that not only looks good but also provides a superb user experience. In today's digital age, your website is often the first important means of communication between your business and potential customers.
            </p>

            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A user-friendly website is essential for creating a positive first impression, building trust, and converting visitors into loyal customers. But what makes a website truly user-friendly? And how do top web development companies like <strong>Web EASY Experts</strong> ensure that your website meets these standards?</p>

            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <h2 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h2" id="what-is">What is a User-Friendly Website?</h2>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A user-friendly website is easy to use, visually appealing, and optimised for speed and performance. It's a website that guides the user intuitively, allowing them to find what they need quickly and effortlessly. Whether you need a custom e-commerce website, a real estate website, or a professional service website, ensuring user-friendliness is key to success.</p>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tip">
              <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i>
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-tip-text"><strong>Quick Check:</strong> Is your website user-friendly? A simple test — if a first-time visitor can find your contact info within 10 seconds, you're off to a great start.</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <h2 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h2" id="tips">Best Tips for Creating a User-Friendly Website</h2>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">An attractive, user-friendly website is not only a requirement now; it's a necessity. A good-looking design is only part of having a positive experience for visitors. A visitor will stay longer and take action if they can navigate easily and find what they need quickly.</p>

            <!-- Responsive Design -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-phone" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Responsive Design for All Devices</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Most users are accessing the web via mobile devices, so it's essential that your website change based on the screen size. A responsive design ensures the same look, feel, and function across all devices — smartphones, tablets, laptops, and desktops.</p>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Optimizing your site's layouts, images, and buttons helps customers navigate and interact with content — this is especially crucial for e-commerce websites where many users buy from their phones.</p>

            <!-- Performance -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-speedometer2" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Test and Optimize Performance</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A good website goes beyond simply being well-designed; it should also perform effectively. Test your website on multiple devices and browsers to catch issues before users do.</p>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box">
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box-title">Speed Tips That <span>Actually Work</span></div>
              <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list">
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Compress and optimise all images before uploading</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Minify CSS, JavaScript, and HTML files</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Use caching and Content Delivery Networks (CDNs)</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Improve server response times with good hosting</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Reduce unnecessary third-party scripts and plugins</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Navigation -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-compass" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Simplify Navigation and User Flow</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Your website should not leave visitors feeling lost. The ability to navigate around your website easily and intuitively is critical to avoid confusion. Create a logical organisation of pages and guide visitors along a natural path — from arrival to completing their goal.</p>

            <!-- Menus -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-list-ul" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Use Clear and Concise Menus</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">The menu of your site is among the key components of your overall website. Make sure menus are not too cluttered, and use simple, descriptive labels that make sense to your customers.</p>

            <!-- Content -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-file-text" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Create Readable and Relevant Content</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Content plays a major role in user experience. Keep your writing simple, clear, and easy to scan. Use:</p>
            <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-list">
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Short paragraphs that are easy to digest</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Clear headings and subheadings to guide the reader</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Bullet points where needed to highlight key info</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-cursor-fill" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Optimize Call-to-Actions (CTA)</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Every website should guide users toward a specific action — whether it's making a purchase, signing up, or contacting you. Place your call-to-action buttons strategically and use clear, direct language like <em>"Get Started," "Contact Us,"</em> or <em>"Buy Now."</em></p>

            <!-- SEO -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-search" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Implement SEO Best Practices</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A user-friendly website should also be easy to find. Focus on:</p>
            <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-list">
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Optimised page titles and meta descriptions</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Relevant keywords used naturally throughout the content</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Clean, readable URL structure</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Accessibility -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3"><i class="bi bi-universal-access" style="color:#E53935;margin-right:0.4rem"></i> Ensure Accessibility for All Users</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A truly user-friendly website is accessible to everyone, including people with disabilities. Follow best practices such as:</p>
            <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-list">
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Adding alt text to all images</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Maintaining proper colour contrast throughout</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Enabling full keyboard navigation</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-divider"></div>

            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <h2 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h2" id="how-we-help">How Web EASY Experts Boost User Experience</h2>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">At Web EASY Experts, we apply a combination of strategy, technology, and user insight to create high-performing websites. Here's how we enhance user experience at every stage:</p>

            <!-- Understanding -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Understanding Your Business and Users</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Before starting any design or development work, our team takes time to understand your business goals, target audience, and user expectations. This step is essential because a user-friendly website is built around the needs of its visitors.</p>

            <!-- Industry cards -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Tailored Solutions for Different Industries</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Every industry has different user expectations, and a one-size-fits-all approach simply doesn't work. That's why solutions are customised based on the type of business:</p>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-cards-grid">
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card">
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon mi-blue"><i class="bi bi-building"></i></div>
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-title">Real Estate Websites</div>
                <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-desc">Advanced search filters, detailed property listings, and virtual tours — making it easy for users to explore and compare options quickly.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card">
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon mi-green"><i class="bi bi-heart-pulse"></i></div>
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-title">Medical Websites</div>
                <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-desc">Focused on simplicity and accessibility, with easy appointment booking, clear service info, and secure patient interactions.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card">
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon mi-amber"><i class="bi bi-bag-check"></i></div>
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-title">E-commerce Websites</div>
                <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-desc">Built for smooth navigation, fast loading, and secure checkout — helping users browse and buy without friction.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card">
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-icon mi-red"><i class="bi bi-briefcase"></i></div>
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-title">Professional Services</div>
                <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-card-desc">Structured to highlight expertise, showcase portfolios, and provide clear contact options for potential clients.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right technology -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Using the Right Technology for Better Experience</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">By working with modern tools like <strong>Shopify, WordPress, Wix, Squarespace, and Webflow</strong>, websites are built to be fast, flexible, and easy to manage. The focus is on optimising these platforms to improve usability — ensuring faster load times, clean layouts, and smooth interactions across all devices.</p>

            <!-- Ecommerce -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Creating Seamless E-commerce Experiences</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">For online stores, user experience directly impacts sales. Key improvements include:</p>
            <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-list">
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Clear product categories and filters</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Simple and secure checkout process</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Mobile-optimised design throughout</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-diamond-fill"></i> Fast-loading product pages</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Consistency -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Ensuring Consistency Across Devices</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Users switch between devices constantly, so maintaining consistency is crucial. Websites are designed to perform equally well on smartphones, tablets, and desktops — no matter how users access the site, they receive the same smooth and reliable experience.</p>

            <!-- Continuous testing -->
            <h3 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h3">Continuous Testing and Improvement</h3>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">User experience doesn't end after launch. Regular testing across devices and browsers helps identify issues and improve performance over time. By analysing user behaviour and making ongoing adjustments, the website continues to evolve and deliver better results.</p>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-divider"></div>

            <!-- Why choose section -->
            <h2 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h2" id="why-choose">Why Choose Web EASY Experts?</h2>

            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box">
              <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-box-title">What Sets Us <span>Apart</span></div>
              <ul class="wbeasy-blog-pg-dark-list">
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <strong style="color:#E2E8F0">Proven Track Record</strong> — Expertise across e-commerce, real estate, medical, and professional service websites</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <strong style="color:#E2E8F0">Custom Solutions</strong> — Tailored website design for every business size and type</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <strong style="color:#E2E8F0">Dedicated Team</strong> — Passionate professionals committed to excellence in every project</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <strong style="color:#E2E8F0">Full Digital Marketing</strong> — SEO, PPC, social media marketing and more, all under one roof</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Conclusion -->
            <h2 class="wbeasy-blog-pg-h2" id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">A user-friendly website is vital for any business that wants to succeed online. Web EASY Experts creates websites that look great, are easy to use, and load lightning fast — while also being search engine optimised.</p>
            <p class="wbeasy-blog-pg-p">Whether you require an e-commerce site, a real estate site, or a small business website, Web EASY Experts has a solution for you. They build on all major platforms: <strong>Shopify, Squarespace, WordPress, Wix, one.com, and Webflow</strong> — making them your best choice for design and development.</p>

            <!-- Bottom bar -->
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-bottom-bar">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <span class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-label">Share</span>
                <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btns">
                  <button class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn" title="Share on Facebook"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></button>
                  <button class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn" title="Share on Twitter/X"><i class="bi bi-twitter-x"></i></button>
                  <button class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn" title="Share on LinkedIn"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></button>
                  <button class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn" title="Share on WhatsApp"><i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i></button>
                  <button class="wbeasy-blog-pg-share-btn" title="Copy link"><i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i></button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <a href="#contact" class="wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-btn">
                <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff-fill"></i> Get a Free Audit
              </a>
            </div>

          </div><!-- /body -->
        </article>
      </div><!-- /col -->

      <!-- ── Sidebar ── -->
      <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="600" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-sidebar-sticky">
        <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-sidebar">

          <!-- CTA widget -->
          <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget">
            <div class="wbeasy-blog-pg-cta-widget-icon"><i class="bi bi-stars"></i></div>
